{"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeBulletListComponentTokensProvider"]]},"sections":[],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeBulletListComponentTokensProvider\/TokensProvider-Implementations","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"Theme Orange"}],"title":"TokensProvider Implementations","roleHeading":"API Collection","role":"collectionGroup"},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemebulletlistcomponenttokensprovider\/tokensprovider-implementations"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"topicSections":[{"generated":true,"title":"Instance Methods","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeBulletListComponentTokensProvider\/checkInstances(count:for:)"],"anchor":"Instance-Methods"}],"kind":"article","references":{"ic_theme_orange.png":{"type":"image","identifier":"ic_theme_orange.png","alt":null,"variants":[{"url":"\/images\/OUDSThemesOrange\/ic_theme_orange.png","traits":["1x","light"]}]},"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange/OrangeThemeBulletListComponentTokensProvider":{"url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemebulletlistcomponenttokensprovider","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeThemeBulletListComponentTokensProvider"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeThemeBulletListComponentTokensProvider"}],"role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeBulletListComponentTokensProvider","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A class which wraps all "},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"component  tokens of bullet list"}]},{"type":"text","text":" for "},{"typ